data.description: Welcome to the beautiful Waterleaf community, where this exceptional single family home, located on a corner lot awaits you. Step inside and be greeted by the tasteful design and modern finishes. Its beautiful kitchen boasts sleek stainless steel appliances, complemented by elegant upgraded granite countertops. The staggered crown molded cabinets provide ample storage space while adding a touch of sophistication to the heart of the home. The spacious living areas combine style and durability for everyday living. Every detail has been carefully considered, including the modern automated smart home system, which allows for seamless control of various features and enhances the overall convenience and efficiency of your daily routine. The outdoor lanai has a roll down shade to enjoy your morning cup of coffee or to relax with a book. The backyard is fully enclosed with a beautiful wrought iron/PVC fence for you to entertain family and friends or dogs to roam and play. The gated Waterleaf community itself offers an abundance of recreational amenities. Take advantage of the clubhouse, cool off in the refreshing pool, let your furry friends roam freely in the dog park, or explore the fitness trails for an invigorating workout. Basketball courts and a playground provide additional options for outdoor activities, ensuring there's something for everyone to enjoy. Best of all, the HOA includes Ultra-fi internet, cable and lawn maintenance. Convenience is paramount in this location, as the property is situated near hospitals, schools, shopping centers, restaurants, and more. This property embodies the perfect blend of luxury, convenience, and a highly desired community. Don't miss your chance to make this wonderful residence your own. Schedule a private showing today and discover the home you've been dreaming of.
